T02TD2825E:173a-0: @173a * // 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs gzhan gyis mi thub pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2825E:173a-1: padma r'a ga byi ru mi ltar kun nas rab 'bar 'od 'phro'i sku //
T02TD2825E:173a-2: padmo nyi zla bgegs rnams mgo mnan mi bzad rngam pa'i sku chen po //
T02TD2825E:173a-3: zhal gsum phyag drug spyan stong mnga' ba'i rgyal ba dpa' bo 'jigs shing rab 'jigs bzhad pa po //
T02TD2825E:173a-4: g-yas dkar g-yon sngo dbus dmar dmar ba'i zhal ldan de bzhin ral gri mchog dang dgra sta dang //
T02TD2825E:173a-5: sdigs mdzub dang ni dril bu zhags bcas tshangs pa'i mgo bsnams stag gi pags pas smad g-yogs pa //
T02TD2825E:173a-6: bskal pa'i me ltar ye shes 'bar ba'i rlabs 'khrugs rab tu 'jigs pa'i 'ur sgra can //
T02TD2825E:173a-7: khrag gis zhal bkang nga ro mi bzad sgra sgrogs sprul gdug khros pas sku rab brgyan //
T02TD2825E:173a-8: dbang bdag brgyad cu'i mgo bo rlon pas do shal phreng thogs brdabs pa'i gad rgyangs 'byin pa'o //
T02TD2825E:173a-9: lha 'di dpa' bo dpa' chen po //
T02TD2825E:173a-10: bdud kyi dgra las rnam rgyal zhing //
T02TD2825E:173a-11: gzhan gyis mi thub mthu bo che //
T02TD2825E:173a-12: pha rol dpung rnams 'joms pa yin //
T02TD2825E:173a-13: sngags pa gang zhig nad dang dgra //
T02TD2825E:173a-14: sngon bsags bsod nams ma yin dang //
T02TD2825E:173a-15: sna tshogs mya ngan 'jigs rnams las //
T02TD2825E:173a-16: sgrol ba mi pham sbyor ba 'di //
T02TD2825E:173a-17: rnal 'byor brtson par byed pa des //
T02TD2825E:173a-18: zla ba drug ni lon pa dang //
T02TD2825E:173a-19: stag dang seng ge glang chen dang //
T02TD2825E:173a-20: mkha' lding nor bu sgron mthong 'gyur //
T02TD2825E:173a-21: de tshe snying dkyil pad dmar gyi //
T02TD2825E:173a-22: 'dab drug yi ge drug dgod bya //
T02TD2825E:173a-24: de yis de dbus snying po yi //
T02TD2825E:173a-25: snying po sa bon hr'i: 'phros pa'o //
T02TD2825E:173a-27: tshul gyis zhag bdun bzlas nas ni //
T02TD2825E:173a-28: gang gang bzlog pa de bsgrub pas //
T02TD2825E:173a-29: las de la ni sbyar bar bya //
T02TD2825E:173a-30: las gang yang dag grub 'grub pa //
T02TD2825E:173b-0: de nyid skye bo @173b gzhan la yang //
T02TD2825E:173b-1: sngags dang ting 'dzin phyag rgya dang //
T02TD2825E:173b-2: khrus kyi cho ga sbyin pa yi //
T02TD2825E:173b-3: glo bur ring por mi thogs par //
T02TD2825E:173b-4: ma lus dbang du 'gyur bar bshad //
T02TD2825E:173b-5: gzhan las rnam par rgyal ba'i gdams ngag rdzogs so//
